      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S represents the pinnacle of the 996 chassis, featuring the iconic wide-body silhouette and Turbo-spec suspension geometry. Powered by a 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus, the power delivery is linear and urgent across the rev range. The G96 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise, tactile engagement, while the viscous-clutch AWD system ensures exceptional mechanical grip. This specimen is in concours-level condition: the factory Arctic Silver finish is flawless, and the interior retains its original matte texture with zero bolster wear. Mechanically optimized with a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh RMS, this C4S is free of bore scoring and ready for high-performance duty.",
